* 初始化环境

- GOROOT 放置go的标准库和工具链
$HOME/local/go (linux, mac) 
c:\local\go (windows) 

- GOPATH 放置第三方代码和自己的工程
$HOME/go (linux, mac) 
c:\go (windows)

- PATH
export PATH=$GOROOT/bin:$GOPATH/bin:$PATH

